# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:327
msgid ""
"Note: Pay close attention to the play-head position (red playback line). Key "
"frames are automatically created at the current playback position, to help "
"quickly create animations. If you want to transform a clip with **no "
"animation**, be sure the playhead is positioned before (to the left) of your "
